      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i'm stuck on this circuit problem for my lab. i have a series circuit with a 12V AC source, a 50 ohm resistor, and an inductor that has an inductive reactance of 30 ohms. how do i calculate the total impedance of the circuit? just need the steps if u can",
